thread.title_full: The House of Bachelorette reviewed by Susan P

author: Susan P
title: Susan P
text: Everything I ordered is exactly as described. Shopping was fast. Packaged nicely and the packing list was even signed with a short message. Nice to have a human touch included. I am looking forward the party. Would definitely recommend this site to anyone looking for fun party items.
